13/ty-article/.premium/the-last-chance-summit-for-an-israel-hamas-deal/00000191-47eb-d8c7-a59d-57ef607d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：伊朗、真主党威胁下没有新的紧急措施；白宫预计以色列可能遭受“重大”袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article-live/idf-no-new-emergency-measures-white-house-warns-of-possible-significant-attack/00000191-4989-d633-a393-cdbf127d0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦报道：西岸袭击事件中的枪手在11月人质协议中被公布 ■ 以色列国防军表示正在审查哈马斯关于一名以色列人质被绑架者枪杀的说法 ■ 西方领导人在声明中支持“以色列防御伊朗侵略” ■ 美国主要学术联盟撤回反对意见抵制以色列大学 ■ 约250名以色列人参加加沙边境的右翼祈祷集会，呼吁重新安置</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 02:28:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article-live/idf-no-new-emergency-measures-white-house-warns-of-possible-significant-attack/00000191-4989-d633-a393-cdbf127d0000</guid></item><item><title>卡马拉·哈里斯的竞选团队任命出生于耶路撒冷的伊兰·戈登伯格作为美国犹太社区的联络人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/kamala-harris-campaign-taps-ilan-goldenberg-as-liaison-to-u-s-jewish-community/00000191-489a-d1ef-afd1-daff06a40000</link><description>任命之际，副总统因其对加沙战争的态度以及美国对以色列的军事援助而面临来自左派的持续压力，而共和党人继续将民主党对以色列的分歧武器化</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 22:18:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/kamala-harris-campaign-taps-ilan-goldenberg-as-liaison-to-u-s-jewish-community/00000191-489a-d1ef-afd1-daff06a40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列计划在 10 月 7 日的纪念活动中纳入活人质，家人对此感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/families-fume-over-israels-plans-to-include-living-hostages-in-october-7-memorial-events/00000191-4834-d1cf-a5dd-ce7cf2d20000</link><description>那些仍被哈马斯关押且命运不明的以色列人的亲属拒绝接受该国在他们的亲人被绑架周年纪念日“纪念”的计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 21:45:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/families-fume-over-israels-plans-to-include-living-hostages-in-october-7-memorial-events/00000191-4834-d1cf-a5dd-ce7cf2d20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列博物馆为伊朗袭击做好准备，马格利特和伦勃朗的杰作得到庇护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/magritte-rembrandt-masterpieces-take-shelter-as-israel-museum-braces-for-iranian-attack/00000191-47ce-d0da-afb1-57dfb0d00000</link><description>正如加沙战争初期所做的那样，耶路撒冷机构将其一些“最重要”的作品放置在受保护的空间中。特拉维夫艺术博物馆也采取了类似措施</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 19:11:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/magritte-rembrandt-masterpieces-take-shelter-as-israel-museum-braces-for-iranian-attack/00000191-47ce-d0da-afb1-57dfb0d00000</guid></item><item><title>美国主要学术联盟撤回抵制以色列大学的反对意见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/major-u-s-academic-union-withdraws-opposition-to-boycotting-israeli-universities/00000191-479d-d732-adf5-c7bdc9590000</link><description>虽然美国大学教授协会的声明没有具体提及以色列，但加沙战争很可能是其在近二十年后重新审视其政策的原因。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 17:56:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/major-u-s-academic-union-withdraws-opposition-to-boycotting-israeli-universities/00000191-479d-d732-adf5-c7bdc9590000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 311 天：据报道真主党撤离贝鲁特总部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-311-hezbollah-reportedly-evacuates-beirut-headquarters/00000191-474c-d1cf-a5dd-cf7c0ab20000</link><description>伊朗外长表示，伊朗有权对以色列采取“适当和威慑性反应”，以确保地区稳定 ■ 法国、德国、英国呼吁伊朗及其盟友不要发动可能危及加沙停战谈判的袭击 ■ 以色列国防部长致电内塔尼亚胡“全面胜利”口号“无稽之谈” ■ 福克斯新闻报道称，伊朗可能在 24 小时内袭击以色列 ■ 战争已过去 311 天，您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 16:31:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-311-hezbollah-reportedly-evacuates-beirut-headquarters/00000191-474c-d1cf-a5dd-cf7c0ab20000</guid></item><item><title>为什么 AIPAC 没有公开试图推翻伊尔汗·奥马尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-12/ty-article/.highlight/why-aipac-hasnt-publicly-tried-to-unseat-ilhan-omar/00000191-472b-db9a-a197-d7ef45540000</link><description>奥马尔与众议员拉希达·特莱布和亚历山大·奥卡西奥-科尔特斯一样，仍然受到选民的欢迎，并且没有选举上的弱点，而正是这些弱点使美国公共事务委员会能够帮助纽约的鲍曼和密苏里州的布什下台。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 16:27:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-12/ty-article/.highlight/why-aipac-hasnt-publicly-tried-to-unseat-ilhan-omar/00000191-472b-db9a-a197-d7ef45540000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在驳回有关加沙战争“全面胜利”的言论后猛烈抨击国防部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-blasts-defense-minister-after-he-dismisses-talk-of-total-victory-in-gaza-war/00000191-4701-d7bb-a1df-ef6bd40a0000</link><description>国防部长约夫·加兰特对议会委员会表示，“我听到英雄们敲响了战争的鼓声，‘全面胜利’和胡言乱语”，促使总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡指责他采取了“反以色列的叙述”</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 15:53:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-blasts-defense-minister-after-he-dismisses-talk-of-total-victory-in-gaza-war/00000191-4701-d7bb-a1df-ef6bd40a0000</guid></item><item><title>汉莎航空和瑞士航空将暂停飞往以色列的航班至少延长至 8 月 21 日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/lufthansa-and-swiss-extend-suspension-of-flights-to-israel-until-at-least-august-21/00000191-46e7-d7bb-a1df-efef150e0000</link><description>汉莎航空将延长飞往多个中东目的地的航班暂停时间，包括特拉维夫、贝鲁特、安曼和伊拉克埃尔比勒</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 14:32:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/lufthansa-and-swiss-extend-suspension-of-flights-to-israel-until-at-least-august-21/00000191-46e7-d7bb-a1df-efef150e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队拘留两名在约旦河西岸前哨袭击阿拉伯裔以色列妇女的嫌疑人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-detain-two-suspects-for-assaulting-arab-israeli-women-at-west-bank-outpost/00000191-46c5-d7bb-a1df-efefe3f20000</link><description>《Shin Bet》称，两名被捕者涉嫌投掷石块、持武器威胁以及纵火焚烧女子汽车，将于明天举行听证会以延长拘留期限</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 14:25:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-detain-two-suspects-for-assaulting-arab-israeli-women-at-west-bank-outpost/00000191-46c5-d7bb-a1df-efefe3f20000</guid></item><item><title>数百名以色列人聚集在加沙边境祈祷集会，敦促加沙地带重新定居</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/idf-closes-swath-of-highways-near-gaza-border-in-lead-up-to-mass-prayer/00000191-464b-dbfd-a7f3-7f6ff2dc0000</link><description>这次祈祷集会是由定居者团体在犹太斋戒日 Tisha B&amp;#39;Av 之前组织的，预计将吸引超过 300 名参加者。 “我们有 600 多个家庭准备搬到这里。我们迫不及待地希望战争结束”，一位参与者说</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 11:50:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/idf-closes-swath-of-highways-near-gaza-border-in-lead-up-to-mass-prayer/00000191-464b-dbfd-a7f3-7f6ff2dc0000</guid></item><item><title>消息来源：哈马斯拒绝新提议并不意味着与以色列的谈判破裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/sources-hamas-rejection-of-new-proposals-doesnt-indicate-collapse-of-talks-with-israel/00000191-4601-dcc2-a9d1-4ed94e380000</link><description>哈马斯呼吁调解人提出一项计划，从四月份开始实施拜登大纲，而不是提出任何关于人质/停火协议的新提议，这主要被视为一种战术举措，旨在在与以色列恢复谈判之前施加压力。至来源</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 10:37:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/sources-hamas-rejection-of-new-proposals-doesnt-indicate-collapse-of-talks-with-israel/00000191-4601-dcc2-a9d1-4ed94e380000</guid></item><item><title>值得吗？关于以色列袭击中东的十大紧迫问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/was-it-worth-it-ten-burning-questions-about-israels-attacks-in-the-middle-east/00000191-45d8-d49b-a7f7-6ddc78730000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 09:43:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/was-it-worth-it-ten-burning-questions-about-israels-attacks-in-the-middle-east/00000191-45d8-d49b-a7f7-6ddc78730000</guid></item><item><title>在最初的失败之后，以色列军队正在研究挽救极端正统派男子征召动力的方法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/after-initial-failures-idf-examines-ways-to-salvage-drive-to-draft-ultra-orthodox-men/00000191-45cc-debc-a793-4dec2e040000</link><description>以色列国防军人力局正在考虑让极端正统派男子到其常规入伍中心以外的地点报到，以减少他们遇到示威者的机会，并将征召日期分散到更长的时期</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 09:16:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/after-initial-failures-idf-examines-ways-to-salvage-drive-to-draft-ultra-orthodox-men/00000191-45cc-debc-a793-4dec2e040000</guid></item><item><title>前以色列国防军将军转为政治家的亚伊尔·戈兰：“不确定”以色列是否是一个民主国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/former-idf-deputy-chief-says-he-is-not-sure-israel-is-a-democracy-anymore/00000191-457b-dcc2-a9d1-4ffb78d50000</link><description>以色列新成立的中左翼政党民主党党魁亚伊尔·戈兰在接受《卫报》采访时表示支持两国解决方案，但强调这一过程可能需要数年时间。 “现在，我们是一个饱受创伤的国家。人们失去了安全感”</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 07:53:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/former-idf-deputy-chief-says-he-is-not-sure-israel-is-a-democracy-anymore/00000191-457b-dcc2-a9d1-4ffb78d50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting/00000191-44f7-d621-a3db-d6f7137f0000</link><description>以色列国防军确认这名士兵是 19 岁的中士。 Omer Ginzburg，一名来自以色列北部的 19 岁伞兵</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 05:14:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting/00000191-44f7-d621-a3db-d6f7137f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：伊朗、真主党威胁下没有新的紧急措施；白宫预计以色列可能遭受“重大”袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/20